Citi Bike Unveils Manhattan Expansion Plan New stations could appear as far north as 86th Street this year By andrew.tangel@wsj.com July 13, 2015 9:11 p.m. ET 
Citi Bike is heading uptown, with a broad expansion that could bring its docking stations as far as midway up Central Park this year.
